# Abstract Streamer Bot 🍅

A Telegram bot that sends notifications when Abstract streamers go live. Built with Otomato SDK for growth hacking.

## Quick Setup

### 1. Get Your Tokens

**Telegram Bot:**
1. Message [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather)
2. Send `/newbot`
3. Follow instructions and copy your token

**Otomato Token:**
1. Visit: https://secret-echinodon-f5b.notion.site/How-to-use-the-SDK-Somnia-edition-20f268c3f22980ba8452caea7d377b2c
2. Follow the guide to generate your token

### 2. Install & Run

```bash
# Clone/download the files
# Create these files: package.json, bot.js, .env.example, .gitignore

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Setup environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your actual tokens

# Start the bot
npm start

# For development (auto-restart)
npm run dev
```

## Bot Commands

```
/start - Get started
/add <streamer> - Add streamer to watch  
/remove <streamer> - Remove streamer
/list - Show your streamers
/toggle - Turn notifications on/off
```

## Files You Need

```
abstract-streamer-bot/
├── package.json     # Dependencies
├── bot.js          # Main bot code  
├── .env.example    # Environment template
├── .env            # Your actual tokens (create this)
├── .gitignore      # Git ignore
└── README.md       # This file
```

## Example Usage

```
User: /start
Bot: 🍅 Welcome to Abstract Streamer Notifications!

User: /add ninja
Bot: ✅ Added ninja to your watchlist!

User: /list  
Bot: 📺 Your Streamers (1):
     • ninja
     Notifications: 🔔 ON
```

When `ninja` goes live → Bot sends: "🔴 ninja is live! 🎮 Watch now: https://portal.abs.xyz/stream/ninja"

## Growth Hacking

Every notification includes "Made with ❤️ by Otomato" to drive users to discover the platform and build their own automations.

## Deploy

**Railway:**
1. Connect GitHub repo to Railway
2. Add environment variables in dashboard
3. Deploy!

**Heroku:**
```bash
heroku create your-bot-name
heroku config:set TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_token
heroku config:set OTOMATO_TOKEN=your_token  
git push heroku main
```

